Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the legendary Snow Woman!\NA heart-chilling and sad case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Snow Woman Legend Murder Case."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Genbee Ski Lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though my body may die,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,know that my spirit will\Nsomeday be revived with the snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:21.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Love of the Snow Woman - To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always such a powerful show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mechanical doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doll, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really well-made!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a rare thing you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The previous owners of this place left it behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:51.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lodge Owner\NGenbee's Wife
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you watching\Nthe Snow Woman on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Snow Women aren't for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This area is famous for\Nits Snow Woman sightings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows, maybe she'll\Neven show up tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really staying here, Yoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:19.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita Akiko (26) Actress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this a "great inn"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no other place to stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:23.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Asanuma Yoko (26) Actress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the bus already left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! I made a\Nreservation the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes! Kinoshita Akiko-{\i1}san\N{\i0}and Asanuma Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0}, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming all this way!\NYour skis have already arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Did you just say\N"Kinoshita Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's really you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just watching\N"Love of the Snow Woman" on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! It's Kinoshita Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nthe actress! In the flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mori Kogoro, the detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That scene where you throw\Nyourself into the lake was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell straight for\Nthe lake, like, "Whoosh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was actually Yoko\Nwho did that dive, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a stuntwoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you act out dangerous\Nscenes in the place of main actors?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko is my exclusive stuntwoman.\NMy double, you could even say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, where might the\Nrestroom be? It's so chilly outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the restroom is--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the far end of\Nthe hall, on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does our room have\Na view of a persimmon tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just as you requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hit the hay, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}. Yoko-{\i1}san\N{\i0}said this is her first time here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how did she know\Nwhere the bathroom was?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're so curious\Nabout everything, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't bathrooms usually\Nalways in the same general area?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially in older buildings like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the weather is clear tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The Snow Woman!\NConan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! The Snow Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The Snow Woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be! I saw her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! I saw the Snow Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Snow Woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just so\Nafraid of the Snow Woman
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that a pile of snow\Nlooked like her to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It was just my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'll be back tomorrow evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd like to schedule\Na body massage and a facial!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}. Don't forget these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost look like a bank robber gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actresses can't afford to be sunburned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There's Yoko-{\i1}san {\i0}and Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain weather sure changes fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This snow came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0}! Are you by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}wanted\Nto ski for a little bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}sure is full of power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she pretends to be full of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she's actually not well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}not being well...\NIs she sick somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:07:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Yoko returned yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose she caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real life-saver!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a delicious meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}was coughing.\NIs she all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She doesn't seem\Nto have an appetite, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's resting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss! Can we use the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, go right ahead!\NYou have it to yourselves until 8:00!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take a bath\Nafter 8:00, Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have the\Nmen's bath all to yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}. Are you all right?\NYou really should see a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll do that.\NI think I'll get out for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I think I'll stay in a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say to\Nhaving an after-bath drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so they're making it into a play?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It received such critical acclaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like on TV, Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\Ngoing to play the main character!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you're going to be in it too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but of course!\NPlease come and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'll go to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I guess there\Nwasn't very much in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Conan. Go bring us some beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already 10:00.\NThe owners are asleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some whiskey in\Nmy room, if you'd prefer that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink a little more!\NI'll go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What about the whiskey?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's apparently at\Nthe bottom of Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s suitcase,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she said she'll\Nbring it to us in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0} will?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, still not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I think that is her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whiskey's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ran-{\i1}san{\i0}.\NGo on ahead to the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check on\NAkiko-{\i1}san {\i0}real quick first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't seem to remember that\Ndoll being there when I looked earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh! Did I drink a little too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0} be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Snow Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really did! She was\Nwearing a white kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}! It's terrible! It's Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! It's Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Will
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was gone when I returned to our room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked around the building,\Nbut I couldn't find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when I checked\Nour room closer, I found that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0} has lung cancer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:12:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! But her strange\Ncoughing had her worried, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She says her father\Nsuffered from the same illness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he died of lung cancer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may have been\Nsecretly worried she had cancer too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to die as the Snow Woman..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the Snow Woman I saw just now...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might've been Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0}. Contact the police right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very cold out! We need to\Nfind Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We're going out to\Nsearch, too! Get ready right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, mister! Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}made\Na beauty salon appointment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone committing suicide\Nreally schedule an appointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably decided to kill\Nherself in the spur of the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}was found dead,\Nwearing her Snow Woman costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}! Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no doubt\Nshe is Kinoshita Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mori Kogoro, a detective.\NI was staying in the same lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Kawada, Mikkamachi Police
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're that famous detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kawada, of the Mikkamachi Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there was a sedative\Nbottle lying next to Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}brought the\Nwhiskey after 10:00 pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning she committed suicide after then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:14:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the Snow Woman\NI saw was probably Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how the scene\Nlooked when we found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?! Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since this was a suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,help from the Great Detective\NMori probably won't be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signs that someone climbed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. Where is the previous\Nowner of this lodge now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The previous owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He lives in the next village over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was no suicide! It was a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the killer was that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to send the body\Noff for mandatory autopsy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's pretty clear it's a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not take that body away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinoshita Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s death\Nwas a murder, not a suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}! What evidence do\Nyou have it was a murder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Kawada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closer at the photographs\Nfrom when her body was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s hair is inside\Nthe collar of the kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A person seeking out death\Nwouldn't wear clothes so brazenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone changed her clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, Asanuma Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}! You know Akiko-{\i1}san\N{\i0}wasn't in a normal state of mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she worried about her\Nhair when putting on the kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Kawada.\NPlease look at the photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears her body was\Nburied quite deeply in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The snow started yesterday around\N5:00 pm and ended around 8:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}had killed\Nherself after 10:00 last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her body wouldn't have\Nbeen buried in that much snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one other thing.\NLook closely at Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a foundation on to prevent sunburn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone at night,\Nand someone about to commit suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,really put such a foundation on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she does have foundation on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}was most likely given\Nthe sedative without her realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And no one else but you\Ncould have done that, Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}! You all\Nsaw Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we saw was\Nyou acting as Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Acting?! What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one\Nwho invited Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}skiing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and booked a room here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you choose this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it would be easiest\Nto play two people at once here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two people at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}share similar stature.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After killing her, you needed\Nto make it appear she was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you chose this lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't this Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s first time here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worked here part-time one\Nwinter during your student days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The previous owner\Nremembered your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, you gave her\Nthe sedative to knock her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You then put her in her Snow\NWoman outfit and left her outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky for you, it had just started to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what you didn't count on\Nwas the snow stopping soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. The Snow Woman you\Nsaw our first day here was Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She covered herself with a white\Nkimono to keep from standing out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as she went to hide another kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were two Snow Woman outfits:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one for Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}and one\Nfor Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0}, the stuntwoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She buried one of\Nthem in the snow in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the following day,\Nyesterday evening to be precise,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she put it on the sleeping Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you returned here\Nas if nothing had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0} came back, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You disguised yourself as her\Nas soon as you returned to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make it seem like the\Ndead Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}was still quite alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You climbed to the roof via the\Npersimmon tree outside your window.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a stuntwoman,\Nthat would be simple to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You then put on Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\Nski boots, which you had hidden,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returned with her skis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also played the role of two\Npeople for us in the open-air bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, if anyone, can\Nimitate Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final touch was the\NSnow Woman that Ran saw from the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were pretending to be\NAkiko-{\i1}san {\i0}as she strode off to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make it look like\Nshe had committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that she had still\Nbeen alive at that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the\Nwhiskey she brought us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that was another act of yours.\NWe never saw Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I received the whiskey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Akiko-{\i1}san {\i0}was dead,\Njust who brought the whiskey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You chose this lodge\Nfor one other reason:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the mechanical doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to get the whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you had the\Nmechanical doll bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.48,0:20:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when I went to look,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the doll was nowhere to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't my imagination;
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the doll was actually behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You later returned\Nthe doll to its platform
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when pretending to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you used\Nthe doll to fill in for Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s fingerprints\Nshould be missing from the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's more proof than\Nanything that she no longer existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I drugged Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}... and killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also wrote the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The part about her father's death was true,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was nothing wrong with her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always being outdone by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it to the final audition\Nof my very first drama role,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and lost to Akiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was always the same ever since!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always lose to\Nher in the final audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went on to become a star,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while all I ever heard was,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You look like Kinoshita Akiko.\NWe don't want a copycat show."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:22:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought I'd always be her\Ndouble as long as she was around...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Snow Man! The Snow Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's you, Sachiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.62,0:24:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old guy fell asleep along the way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.67,0:24:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was awake until\N9:00, chatting with Sachiko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her alibi is airtight!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.34,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.28,0:24:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan:\N"Kogoro's Date Murder Case."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.26,0:24:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.81,0:24:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.75,0:24:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode the old man finds himself in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.07,0:24:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why mom left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.18,0:24:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.60,0:24:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
